Lex saw Clark doing his chores in the barn, and briefly contemplated whether confronting him was such a good idea. But, that morning he had asked Chloe what Clark and Lana had to say the previous night and she told him what happened. His blood was boiling. This had to end.<br>
<br>
“You couldn’t leave her alone could you Clark?” Lex asked, his anger rising to the surface.<br>
<br>
